column10: This sheet consolidates the various paths time return on investment, all values are linked from their various original cells for ease of viewing, continue updating the sheets and making adjustments as per your own tower as necessary
Each value in the Time RoI column is the RoI for the next level of the lab
If an RoI is not shown it is likely toggled off on its home path sheet
Copy+Paste the column to the right into your Master Sheet over column C to have the values on the left update the entire book

column19: Similar to the Lab RoI tables copy the column on the right to the Master Sheet (Column M) to be able to update everything from this sheet or copy the column on the left over Column U to update this sheet from the Master Sheet

column10: Copy+Paste the column to the left over column C to have the Master Sheet update this sheet's tables
The Regen table may be ignored unless you have Wall or use WHR
SPB and ITO sum the RoI value from all paths
